Subject: Update Jackson 2.18.6 to 2.18.8 for CVE remediation
Origin: DHI-internal CVE remediation
Reference: https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/com/fasterxml/jackson/core/jackson-databind/2.18.8/
Description: Gradle 9.6.0 pins Jackson 2.18.6 through shared dependency-management
  versions. Bump the 2.18 line to 2.18.8, which fixes CVE-2026-54512,
  CVE-2026-54513, and CVE-2026-54514 without crossing a major or minor Jackson version.

diff --git a/gradle/dependency-management/shared-versions.properties b/gradle/dependency-management/shared-versions.properties
index 4388463228b..fd676aa2c35 100644
--- a/gradle/dependency-management/shared-versions.properties
+++ b/gradle/dependency-management/shared-versions.properties
@@ -17,6 +17,6 @@ asm=9.9!!
 errorProne=2.42.0!!
 groovy=4.0.32!!
-jackson=2.18.6!!
+jackson=2.18.8!!
 kotlinCoroutines=1.10.2!!
 maven=3.9.5!!
 mavenResolver=1.9.16!!
